---
title: Teriyaki-Glazed Pork & Sesame Fries with Cucumber & Apple Salad
description: When teriyaki sauce and a hot pan collide, you get these deliciously caramelised pork loin steaks. Serve them with a refreshing cucumber and apple salad, plus an addition of sesame fries, perfect for soaking up any extra sauce!
